---
/* Aici poți lăsa spațiu pentru logică dacă e nevoie, momentan e curat */
---
<section id="services" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 sm:text-5xl">
        Pachete de Administrare Premium
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Alege nivelul de îngrijire potrivit pentru investiția ta în Torrevieja & Orihuela Costa.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start">
      
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">PEARL 🐚</h3>
          <span class="bg-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold border border-slate-200 uppercase">Basic</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-8">
          <span class="text-4xl font-black text-slate-900">350€</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 font-medium">/an +TVA</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">✔</span> Păstrare chei 24/7</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">✔</span> 1 vizită lunară de control</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">✔</span> Raport foto/video WhatsApp</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">✔</span> Aerisire & verificare robineți</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">✔</span> Verificare post-furtună</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://wa.me/34641477523?text=Salut%20Stelian!%20Vreau%20detalii%20despre%20pachetul%20PEARL." 
           class="block text-center py-4 bg-white border-2 border-slate-900 text-slate-900 font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-900 hover:text-white transition">
           Solicită Pearl
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border-2 border-blue-600 shadow-xl relative md:-mt-4">
        <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
          Cel mai popular
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6 pt-2">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">SAPPHIRE 💙</h3>
          <span class="bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase">Standard Plus</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-8">
          <span class="text-4xl font-black text-slate-900">650€</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 font-medium">/an +TVA</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 text-slate-700">
          <li class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Tot din Pearl +</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">✔</span> 2 vizite lunare detaliate</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">✔</span> Audit Consum (apă/lumină)</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">✔</span> Management IBI & Suma</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">✔</span> Contact Comunitate Vecini</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">✔</span> Gestionare Incident Tehnic</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://wa.me/34641477523?text=Salut%20Stelian!%20Ma%20intereseaza%20pachetul%20SAPPHIRE." 
           class="block text-center py-4 bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-700 transition shadow-lg shadow-blue-200">
           Alege Sapphire
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-emerald-500 shadow-sm transition">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">EMERALD 💚</h3>
          <span class="bg-emerald-900/50 text-emerald-400 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase border border-emerald-500/30">VIP Security</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-8">
          <span class="text-4xl font-black text-white">1500€</span>
          <span class="text-slate-400 font-medium">/an +TVA</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 text-slate-300">
          <li class="text-emerald-400 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Tot din Sapphire +</li>
          <li class="flex items-start font-medium text-white"><span class="text-emerald-400 mr-2">🛡️</span> Protocol Anti-Okupas 48h</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-emerald-400 mr-2">✔</span> Vizite Tactice la 48-72h</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-emerald-400 mr-2">✔</span> Digital Twin (Scanare 360°)</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-emerald-400 mr-2">✔</span> Concierge Pre-Arrival</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-emerald-400 mr-2">✔</span> Priority Support 4h</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://wa.me/34641477523?text=Salut%20Stelian!%20Vreau%20protectie%20maxima%20EMERALD." 
           class="block text-center py-4 bg-emerald-500 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-emerald-600 transition shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/20">
           Rezervă Emerald
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 text-center text-slate-400 text-sm italic">
      *Toate serviciile sunt prestate cu contract legal. Tarifele nu includ IVA (21%).
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
